data.description: The Alabaster's stunning and spacious entry leads to the formal dining, kitchen, and nook that opens to the family room. At the front of the home, the second bedroom with a full bath is perfect for guests. This room can also be an optional study. Enter the spacious owner's suite, tucked away at the back of the home. It features his and her sinks and a large walk-in closet. There are two additional bedrooms upstairs with an optional 5th bedroom. Entertain in the upstairs game room, with the option to add a theater room and an optional powder bath.*Square Footage subject to change due to optional rooms.
